      <h2>Anime: A Global Obsession That Keeps Evolving</h2>
      <p>From the streets of Tokyo to Times Square in New York, anime has become more than a hobby‚Äîit's a cultural movement. In 2025, anime continues to rise in influence, quality, and global reach, fueled by groundbreaking series, passionate communities, and immersive worlds that captivate hearts worldwide.</p>

      <h3>1. The Diversity of Genres Keeps Fans Hooked</h3>
      <p>What makes anime truly unmatched is its sheer diversity. There‚Äôs a story for everyone. From the emotional depths of **Your Lie in April**, to the brutal battles of **Attack on Titan**, or the mind-bending sci-fi of **Steins;Gate**, anime stretches across every genre imaginable:</p>
