      <h3>6. Anime‚Äôs Impact on Culture and Identity</h3>
      <p>Anime is no longer "just cartoons." It shapes fashion, inspires music, and influences film. Artists like Billie Eilish, Bad Bunny, and BTS have spoken about anime‚Äôs effect on their art. And for fans, anime often provides identity, healing, and belonging.</p>

      <h3>7. The Future: What's Next?</h3>
      <p>With AI, AR/VR experiences, and new global studios emerging, anime in 2030 may look completely different‚Äîbut the spirit will remain. Emotionally rich stories, unforgettable characters, and communities built on shared love and excitement.</p>

